column2: select o.objID, d.ra, d.dec, o.raMean, o.decMean, o.raMeanErr, o.decMeanErr, o.qualityFlag, o.nDetections, soa.primaryDetection, soa.bestDetection, soa.gstackDetectID, s.gSerRadius, s.gSerMag, s.gSerAb, s.gSerNu, s.gSerPhi, s.gSerRa, s.gSerDec INTO mydb.ellipticalFits0#  FROM mydb.SNe_TNS_#_PS1_hosts d CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(d.ra, d.dec, #/#) as x JOIN MeanObjectView o on o.ObjID=x.ObjID JOIN StackObjectAttributes AS soa ON soa.ObjID = x.ObjID JOIN StackModelFitSer s ON (s.gstackDetectID=soa.gstackDetectID AND s.ObjID=x.ObjId)
